Great place to have fun with your friends especially if all of you love to sing.  The prices of the beer and other drinks are within our budget range. The place is also well-maintained, you can see some attendants cleaning from time to time. Nice place to have fun

Good karaoke place in a shopping mall.  Nice setup and easy to use web based app.  The only 2 down sides of this place other than the seriously overpriced drinks are that it has no bathroom of it's own which means you need to go out into the mall, and the rooms are not soundproof meaning you can easily be impacted by the noise from your neighbor's

Very clean and system is good. Service also excellent! But I think the songs not very updated. Not much new songs. Hope can have more song choices the next time we visit!!  Definitely will come back again!  üòÅ
Service was excellent, friendly worker! Went with my fiance, the system and songs are up to date too! Affordable price 2pax for 3 hours! Amazing! Will come again soon!
